Proposed Conference on Limitation of Naval Armaments,With reference to Cabinet 9 (25), Conclusion No. 3 of 18th February 1925, I have ascertained that the Government of India have no observations to offer on the draft despatch to Sir Esme Howard in regard to the proposed Conference on the Limitation, of Naval Armaments.4th March 1925. BIRKENHEAD,197 100 3.25
